modules.description: This module provides precise parsing of numeric literals from strings, supporting multiple bases (binary to hexadecimal) and suffixes (n, l, L), while converting them to typed numeric representations like integers, floats, and nativeints with error handling. It enables high-precision use cases such as compiler frontends, financial calculations, or data serialization where exact numeric parsing, rational conversion, or lossless string-to-number roundtrips are critical.
